id: Keira Knightley & Mackenzie Foy Answer the Web's Most Searched Questions
paragraph:

                "The Nutcracker and the Four Realms" stars Keira Knightley and Mackenzie Foy take the WIRED Autocomplete Interview and answer the internet's most searched questions about themselves.
